{"id": "ChIJiz2hv-fbwoARVSjxwtlcXac", "rating": 4.6, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_INEXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 623, "displayName": {"text": "ALittle Tea - San Gabriel", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJiz2hv-fbwoARVSjxwtlcXac/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xadGFFbHRaVE5DVXpoVWVtdDZWV3BvUkU5VlQyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I told this place to give me whatever. So let’s see if they’re pretty good eh or ew. They ended up giving me their mango green milk tea with ice cream and tea jellies and strawberry boba milk tea replace the boba with coconut jellies and add ice cream to try. The mango milk tea was perfectly sweet, milky, and packing with those yummy fruity mangoy flaves. The ice cream made it even creamier and the tea jellies were nice and jiggly. The strawberry milk tea had good light milk tea flaves with the sweet strawberry flaves coming from the puree. The coconut jellies added a nice extra chew and the ice cream added a yummy vanilla creamy sweetness. Even tho this place was poppin People here were super chill, Prices are pretty good for the portions, and you can even get free topping with your drinks. Overall this place is pretty good.\n\nMango green milk tea L w/ toppings $8.49\nStrawberry milk tea L w/ toppings $8.49", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I told this place to give me whatever. So let’s see if they’re pretty good eh or ew. They ended up giving me their mango green milk tea with ice cream and tea jellies and strawberry boba milk tea replace the boba with coconut jellies and add ice cream to try. The mango milk tea was perfectly sweet, milky, and packing with those yummy fruity mangoy flaves. The ice cream made it even creamier and the tea jellies were nice and jiggly. The strawberry milk tea had good light milk tea flaves with the sweet strawberry flaves coming from the puree. The coconut jellies added a nice extra chew and the ice cream added a yummy vanilla creamy sweetness. Even tho this place was poppin People here were super chill, Prices are pretty good for the portions, and you can even get free topping with your drinks. Overall this place is pretty good.\n\nMango green milk tea L w/ toppings $8.49\nStrawberry milk tea L w/ toppings $8.49", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "AC9", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114415861027882176583/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWiFfpOc9nsCcCI97_K0ntJYjx5NEVbNmjYETYfc21YuGhkhUgC=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-24T00:32:27.543851331Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xadGFFbHRaVE5DVXpoVWVtdDZWV3BvUkU5VlQyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xadGFFbHRaVE5DVXpoVWVtdDZWV3BvUkU5VlQyYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2dbe7bfa13d8b:0xa75d5cd9c2f12855"}, {"name": "places/ChIJiz2hv-fbwoARVSjxwtlcXac/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21Wc1QzRlpNVzFGVERkR1kwOTZNaTFtVUY4eVZWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "You can’t beat the price! Affordable and pretty good quality for the price you pay.\nFavorite- passion fruit green tea with tea jelly and most of their fruit teas cost under 5$.\nYou can add a few toppings for free which includes- tea jelly, coffee jelly, boba pearls and pudding. Very popular so be prepared to wait in a line to place an order but the service otherwise quick.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "You can’t beat the price! Affordable and pretty good quality for the price you pay.\nFavorite- passion fruit green tea with tea jelly and most of their fruit teas cost under 5$.\nYou can add a few toppings for free which includes- tea jelly, coffee jelly, boba pearls and pudding. Very popular so be prepared to wait in a line to place an order but the service otherwise quick.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Arpita Biswas", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113226830058210348280/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUzJVmDDm8KY8JfpCDrTlaPlcTohLWhie6hx-PGymUnpy4_iE2-ig=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-02T04:46:58.594831151Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21Wc1QzRlpNVzFGVERkR1kwOTZNaTFtVUY4eVZWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21Wc1QzRlpNVzFGVERkR1kwOTZNaTFtVUY4eVZWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2dbe7bfa13d8b:0xa75d5cd9c2f12855"}, {"name": "places/ChIJiz2hv-fbwoARVSjxwtlcXac/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxSU9FVnljblJXTjBKSlkyODNOMTlyVlVjNWJIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "10 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This boba chain from China is known for two things: quality and affordability. They have a wide variety of drinks, and from my visits, the prices are hard to beat compared to other boba shops in the area.\n\nIt does get pretty packed, so expect a bit of a crowd, especially during peak hours. This time I ordered the Mango Sago with boba at 0% sugar, and it was perfect — just the right amount of natural sweetness without being overpowering.\n\nFor the price and quality, I wouldn’t mind stopping by again whenever I’m in the area. A solid spot if you’re looking for a good drink without breaking the bank.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This boba chain from China is known for two things: quality and affordability. They have a wide variety of drinks, and from my visits, the prices are hard to beat compared to other boba shops in the area.\n\nIt does get pretty packed, so expect a bit of a crowd, especially during peak hours. This time I ordered the Mango Sago with boba at 0% sugar, and it was perfect — just the right amount of natural sweetness without being overpowering.\n\nFor the price and quality, I wouldn’t mind stopping by again whenever I’m in the area. A solid spot if you’re looking for a good drink without breaking the bank.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "William Mao", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112500492720653035867/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8AF3TLQIxu0NqN6Sw7IrIQmiWq2FrHcBsrdiG2ypj-hqkTq8I=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-08-28T22:05:46.068642080Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxSU9FVnljblJXTjBKSlkyODNOMTlyVlVjNWJIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxSU9FVnljblJXTjBKSlkyODNOMTlyVlVjNWJIYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2dbe7bfa13d8b:0xa75d5cd9c2f12855"}, {"name": "places/ChIJiz2hv-fbwoARVSjxwtlcXac/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pKS1pHcERlamMyTFdsSmFtNWxVbDluWTNFeFMxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This was my first time trying this place out and it didn’t disappoint. I was happy to find out they offer a few different free toppings. Most boba places nowadays charge $0.50 to $1.50 for each topping. I also asked if I could get an extra scoop of boba and they gave me a very generous amount. I ordered the oolong milk tea and the quality was very good because they use good quality ingredients. Would definitely come back again.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This was my first time trying this place out and it didn’t disappoint. I was happy to find out they offer a few different free toppings. Most boba places nowadays charge $0.50 to $1.50 for each topping. I also asked if I could get an extra scoop of boba and they gave me a very generous amount. I ordered the oolong milk tea and the quality was very good because they use good quality ingredients. Would definitely come back again.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Christa Mar", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117098594406465912644/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW5Bgd8A9YldFbeCS_VOTh5ru74_u9NLyJmYf8RqKWlTcFLe3AR=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-06T04:07:05.944671970Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pKS1pHcERlamMyTFdsSmFtNWxVbDluWTNFeFMxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pKS1pHcERlamMyTFdsSmFtNWxVbDluWTNFeFMxRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2dbe7bfa13d8b:0xa75d5cd9c2f12855"}, {"name": "places/ChIJiz2hv-fbwoARVSjxwtlcXac/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tZM1QyVmhkMWxwVDBGaWMxbGZiR0Z3YUVjdFMwRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "7 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "REC: Pudding Milk Tea + boba\n\nAffordable without compromising on quality taste and time. While it can get very busy, most of the times they pump out drinks within minutes. They have all three, cashier/counter ordering, self serve kiosk, and online ordering. I personally prefer the kiosk, but to save time I recommend online ordering. Although there is seating inside, it is limited. The outside has a planter edge you can sit on. Drinks can’t be said to be the best, but certainly the price is unbeatable, with most drinks being UNDER $5. If you signed up for rewards, you may also get enough points to get $ off. The store is still pretty new, and inside is simple, but comfortable and nice. Whenever I am in the area and dont feel like dropping $8 for boba, I come here. Def a good spot!\n\nReviewed 11/27/2025", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "REC: Pudding Milk Tea + boba\n\nAffordable without compromising on quality taste and time. While it can get very busy, most of the times they pump out drinks within minutes. They have all three, cashier/counter ordering, self serve kiosk, and online ordering. I personally prefer the kiosk, but to save time I recommend online ordering. Although there is seating inside, it is limited. The outside has a planter edge you can sit on. Drinks can’t be said to be the best, but certainly the price is unbeatable, with most drinks being UNDER $5. If you signed up for rewards, you may also get enough points to get $ off. The store is still pretty new, and inside is simple, but comfortable and nice. Whenever I am in the area and dont feel like dropping $8 for boba, I come here. Def a good spot!\n\nReviewed 11/27/2025", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Xue", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110925827671659266422/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLqSBzVgQJQdqTn8tWsjt84hLalJLk3cMCDk-BGBJJ0EHCLHw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-15T22:05:20.530745670Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tZM1QyVmhkMWxwVDBGaWMxbGZiR0Z3YUVjdFMwRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tZM1QyVmhkMWxwVDBGaWMxbGZiR0Z3YUVjdFMwRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2dbe7bfa13d8b:0xa75d5cd9c2f12855"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJiz2hv-fbwoARVSjxwtlcXac/photos/AWCwydg7kkcZJEfqI-x8gceza7yt_6lsS0Tb6z6Fr1Xk4mQZTi5yCJ9BAtWe0fJquVjDbfxA9mWEh5FdEM_SBwXayHRIC_sg3Eqh_yG6kRBhRnmgu_i3NEfpmiKoLi8V30BhyJ8Qr51kvu_kb9qW9BwgPc5kjjnhO50usDd3Vn8yBUEjHYsIfidRUCW_snRWc4RgiSmcg5oEhwUGJLsWsMJ57Ui96dllsGmx9CbpsQraRGtX42MrZnHM6BYDXe4Ajfn9BUUd7Yl3OqhPG-hvyV7cLWnYFfMo-sbjTLBJKXAaeJLEWQTONIQ1op-NP8AXAc-AOSrk-gsMm2Q3_V1eAA-Fo0NmPkEcP3Pkh93CtFkx-hekG5vT-nRK1_X2kamKGPCZg4oK8F2EOvRNdwOeJj2UjBaAWhAFqdJ8xjHyJrCXgznnmkWh7pw_c401pWiRYYut", "widthPx": 1284, "heightPx": 1587, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Xue", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/110925827671659266422", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLqSBzVgQJ